<h1>=F0=9F=8D=BA Top-down Brew: Mash water strike temperature</h1>
<p><b>Purpose:</b> To calculate the strike water temperature for all-grain =
mashes.</p>
<p>=20
</p><form name=3D"entry">
<input type=3D"number" size=3D"3" maxlength=3D"4" value=3D"1.25" step=3D".1=
