<h2>Notes:</h2>
<p>This calculator determines the temperature of hot water needed to achiev=
e a particular mash temperature. Most mashes are single temperature infusio=
n mashes at a target temperature of <a href=3D"http://howtobrew.com/book/se=
ction-3/the-methods-of-mashing/single-temperature-infusion">150 to 158 fahr=
enheit</a> (66 to 70 celsius). The <a href=3D"http://howtobrew.com/book/sec=
tion-3/the-methods-of-mashing/calculations-for-boiling-water-additions" tar=
get=3D"_blank">formula and additional details</a> are available at John Pal=
mer's howtobrew.com web site. </p>
